info.description: # nh3 ![CI](https://github.com/messense/nh3/workflows/CI/badge.svg) [![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/nh3.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/nh3) [![Documentation Status](https://readthedocs.org/projects/nh3/badge/?version=latest)](https://nh3.readthedocs.io/en/latest/?badge=latest) [ammonia](https://github.com/rust-ammonia/ammonia) Python binding. ## Installation ```bash pip install nh3 ``` ## Usage ```python import nh3 print(nh3.clean("I'm not trying to XSS you")) ``` ## Performance Running on MacBook Air (M2, 2022) ```python Python 3.11.0 (main, Oct 25 2022, 16:25:24) [Clang 14.0.0 (clang-1400.0.29.102)] Type 'copyright', 'credits' or 'license' for more information IPython 8.9.0 -- An enhanced Interactive Python. Type '?' for help. In [1]: import requests In [2]: import bleach In [3]: import nh3 In [4]: html = requests.get("https://www.google.com").text In [5]: %timeit bleach.clean(html) 2.85 ms ± 22.8 µs per loop (mean ± std. dev. of 7 runs, 100 loops each) In [6]: %timeit nh3.clean(html) 138 µs ± 860 ns per loop (mean ± std. dev. of 7 runs, 10,000 loops each) ``` ## License This work is released under the MIT license. A copy of the license is provided in the [LICENSE](./LICENSE) file.
